    "Gemini 1.0 is a new AI model built in three various sizes (Ultra, Pro, and Nano); a result of extensive collaborative efforts of the Google Team, was announced by the Google Team on December 6, 2023, marking a major platform upgrade.",
    "With plans to soon include multimodal reasoning skills, Gemini Pro (Google, https:// gemini. google.",
    "com/ app/) is the first model that is now available and can respond to text-based cues [24].Although Gemini and ChatGPT are comparable in several ways, Gemini has a remarkable aptitude for comprehending and responding to inquiries that need for exact details, while, on the other hand, ChatGPT may effectively produce a wide range of imaginative and varied texts, including articles, scripts, code, and more, all of which may or may not be entirely correct [22].",
    "Chatbot-aided surgical choiceWe entered every case description into either ChatGPT (version 3.5) or Google Gemini interface.",
    "Both platforms were accessed on March 8 and 9, 2024."
